    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "In our college all students eligible for placements but who have backlogs more than 3 they are don't eligible for placements. In our college so many companies cone to recruit the students. Average package is 4 LPA.",
          "name": "Devandla Srikanth",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "what really stands out about QISCET is the emphasis on extracurricular activities and student clubs.",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "In our college infrastructure is good with computer labs and workshop with proper equipment and all departments have proper lab equipment with well trained lab assistant.",
          "name": "Devandla Srikanth",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "This college has club activities for everyday like dance,sports,film,etc.This makes students to go on their intrest.",
          "name": "Bhavani Prasad S",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "In our college so many social activities are there like NSS and NCC and so many extra curricular activities",
          "name": "Devandla Srikanth",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Qis college encourages student for participating in college elections and motivate students for extra curricular activities.",
          "name": "Devandla Srikanth",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "College view looks nice with trees and gardens.",
          "name": "Venkateswarlu",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Our college environment is good with nice campus and with gardens",
          "name": "Devandla Srikanth",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "The placement training is excellent and better opportunities are provided.",
          "name": "Bharath",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "In My college there are some cultural activities in my college",
          "name": "Batchu Navya",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Tha average package is only 3.2 lakhs per annum only",
          "name": "YARRABALLI VENKATA VISHNU VARDHAN",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "In our college faculty are less number. That's why some class clashes are there",
          "name": "Devandla Srikanth",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "its hard to get transportation in Night times.",
          "name": "Sunil Tammisetty",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "As the college is situated in rural village reaching is very difficult.",
          "name": "Bharath",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Transportation road to college is not upto level for some distance. We face traffic issues by 5:00pm",
          "name": "Lokesh Kumar Nanganam",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Honestly,the food is a letdown. its like they are serving same old dishes everyday which are inedible. They just need to hire a decent chef or improve kitchen hygiene",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "In our college fees system was some what high with extra fees and fines for late coming",
          "name": "Devandla Srikanth",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "After completion of college there is study hours.",
          "name": "Venkateswarlu",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "College tution fees is high,and condonation fees is also high",
          "name": "Nidamanuri divyeswari",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "In some labs ,the wifi is not good, and some systems are also not working in some labs only",
          "name": "Shaik Nusrath",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        }
